ygData.messageBody:
Are any on the Tornivonnious (sp??) server?  My husband said can you name

Well, my friends and I have all purchased motorcycles and as a result, we al
will be selling our accounts. Here is just a very rough overview of what we
have:

43rd Cleric, Dwarf [male](all twink non plane gear. 199wis, Dark Ember, Belt
of Cenobite, Cleric Bracers, DWB's etc.)
43rd Warrior, Dwarf [male](Wyrmslayer, Shimmering Partisain, FBSS, Mithril
BP, Silver leggings, etc.)
40th Enchanter, Gnome [male](Twinked....Blackened Crystalline robe)
43rd Warrior, Dwarf [female](Wyrmslayer, Cane of Tranquil, FBSS, Mithril BP
etc.)

49th Wizard, High-Elf [female] (stripped)

Let me know if any of these peek your interest.

~Kris


Lena
